<emphasis bold="true" box="[113,556,769,793]" italics="true" pageId="11" pageNumber="326">Distribution and seasonal occurrence. –</emphasis>
<collectingCountry box="[564,662,769,792]" name="Thailand" pageId="11" pageNumber="326">Thailand</collectingCountry>
. Known from one locality in South 
<collectingCountry box="[425,526,801,824]" name="Thailand" pageId="11" pageNumber="326">Thailand</collectingCountry>
. Recorded from the beginning of April in a rain forest.
</paragraph>
